ion Type)\n\nIf it doesn\'t match, we need to prepare a Query document and send it to QG Design Supervisor/PMO and seek clarification','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(355,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','MQMS','SOW','Ensure the job is related to FC+ (COAX_FIBER) or FIA (Fiber Only) job before starting the job.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(356,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','MQMS','Fiber Module','Check and Verify all MQMS modules are as per assigned job type (Fiber Only - FIA).\n(Modules for Fiber Jobs: ROUTE, FIBER, PACKAGE PREP, QC)\nIf the modules are mismatch with assigned job type, then need we need to request the missing module from MQMS.\nIf the modules mismatch with assigned job type, raise a request for the missing module from MQMS.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(357,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','MQMS','Coax+Fiber Modules','Check and Verify all MQMS modules are as per assigned job type (Coax-Fiber - FC+).\n(Modules for Fiber Jobs: ROUTE, COAX, FIBER, PACKAGE PREP, QC)\nIf the modules mismatch with assigned job type, raise a request for the missing module from MQMS.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(358,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','MQMS','Timer','Ensure to start the timer, while creating the assigned job in Magellan.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(359,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','MQMS','Timer','If the job is being rejected back to customer for any reason make sure to record time (a few minutes) on MQMS','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(360,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','MQMS','Route Module','Aerial and UG lengths must always be updated as \"0\" in Route module in MQMS.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(361,'Testing ATX AS-Bui