ng ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','Magellan Tool','Fiber Elements','All Fiber elements must be selected & placed as per the latest and standard guidelines.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(392,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','Magellan Tool','Fiber Elements','Ensure Mux Type, range and Reserved Wavelengths are match as per Fiber information provided in PRISM and Input files.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(393,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','Magellan Tool','Fiber Elements','Fiber splicing/Connectivity must match as per the splicing docs. (Splice matrix, OTDR report, Cus sheets etc. provided in PRISM)','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(394,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','Magellan Tool','Fiber Elements Naming','Naming of the Fiber elements must be as per the latest and standard guidelines.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(395,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','Magellan Tool','Linking','Relink all the Fiber elements to Existing Support elements and length should match as per strand/trench Length in Magellan.\nCheck this point even if Built as Designed job also.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(396,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','Magellan Tool','Linking','Ensure the Address is linked to Fiber Termination box (Business class) for both Forward and Return.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(397,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','Magellan Tool','Verification of Design','Verify all the Fiber Elements (Cable Size, Splitters/Muxes, Splice cases, Business class devices) should match with SOW.\nCheck this point even if Built as Designed job also.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(398,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17: