rs - Centre line, Parcel line and Street Names are enabled.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(409,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','Magellan Tool','Scaling','Match the scaling of all devices in the area.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(410,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','After Deliverables','After Print extraction','Prints must be exported by ensuring the asbuilt area is in the center of the page with all street names layers. \nGenerate the PDF with the help of Lasso Tool only.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(411,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','After Deliverables','Zoom Level','Zoom level must be same as Before Print.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(412,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','After Deliverables','Paper Type','While extracting the prints from Magellan, paper size type must be selected as \"ANSI E\" from the drop down.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(413,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','After Deliverables','STAMP','Screenshot of Design Tab (STAMP) must be taken from PRISM and pasted on the After Print pdf at the top right or top left. \nPlease note Screenshot must cover till the Design Number.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(414,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','After Deliverables','Title Block','Check and Verify the Title Block which has below information is placed in the After Print on 1st page right below the STAMP. It must be clear and legible. \nTitle Block: Node Name, Instance, MAP & AFTER PRINT.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(415,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:55:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',3,'','After Deliverables','Comment Call Out','Check and Verify the asbuilt comment call out should always be as mentione