igner','Once the Designer Name is populated, user must click on \"Assign Designer\" Button in Design Tab.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(457,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:57:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',4,'','Input Validation','Input Files','On PRISM User must navigate to Documents Tab,  Survey document   section and download the file which will has name as \"Asbuilt\" and the attachment type must be \"As-built\". \n\n\"Please note: The file must be of latest date with ASBUILT attachment type.\nIf there is no Asbuilt file under survey document section, reach out to your supervisor for confirmation on rejecting the job.\"','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(458,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:57:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',4,'','Input Validation','Input Files','Downloaded inputs files are legible, readable and clear to understand. \nIf the files are corrupted and unable to understand, then prepare a Query Document and reach out to QG Design Supervisor/PMO and seek clarifications.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(459,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:57:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',4,'','Input Validation','Input Files','Please verify and Ensure the Fiber information is available or not. (Fiber information: Hub Info, Tie point, Mux info etc.)\nIF AUDIT/SPLICING SHEET is not available please reject the job','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(460,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:57:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',4,'','Input Validation','Inputs Comments','Please verify and ensure that Comments mentioned in PRISM Design tab must be Inline with the associated SOW. \nIf it doesn\'t match we need to prepare a query document and send it to QG Design Supervisor/PMO and seek clarification.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(461,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 17:57:07','1644338','SC','SUMMERVILLE','Self QC',4,'','Input Validation','AutoCAD Validation','If the Asbuilt input file is an export from AutoCAD tool and contain