'1605504','NC','KERNERSVILLE','IQC',1,'','Before Print','Before Print','Prints must be taken by ensuring the asbuilt area is in the center of the page with all street names layers. \nGenerate the PDF with the help of Lasso Tool only,','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(821,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 18:11:47','1605504','NC','KERNERSVILLE','IQC',1,'','Before Print','Naming Terminology','Prints must be extracted from Magellan before starting the asbuilt work & must be saved as per Standard naming terminology  at the respective location on the network drive.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(822,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 18:11:47','1605504','NC','KERNERSVILLE','IQC',1,'','Before Print','Paper Type','While extracting the prints from Magellan, paper type must be selected as \"ANSI E\" from the drop down.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(823,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 18:11:47','1605504','NC','KERNERSVILLE','IQC',1,'','Before Print','STAMP','Screenshot of Design Tab (STAMP) must be taken from PRISM and pasted on the Before Print pdf at the  top right or top left.\nPlease note Screenshot must cover till the Design Number.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(824,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 18:11:47','1605504','NC','KERNERSVILLE','IQC',1,'','Before Print','Call Out properties','Check and Verify all the Callout Box (Title Block) properties are as per the Project Specification/Standards. \nRectangle Box with Red Borders & yellow Fill, Text Font: Arial Narrow, BOLD & Text Size: 36.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(825,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 18:11:47','1605504','NC','KERNERSVILLE','IQC',1,'','Before Print','Title Block','Check and Verify the Title Block which has below information is placed in the Before Print on 1st page right below the STAMP. \nTitle Block: Node Name, Instance, Map coordinates, & BEFORE PRINT.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(826,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 18:11:47','1605504','NC','KERNERSVILLE','IQC',1,'','Magellan Tool','Job Creation','Job created on Magellan must have Job Name, description and Region as mentioned below. \nJob Name: MNS_Prism ID_01 \nDescription (Asbuilt Jobs): Fiber Asbuilt, \nDescription (Restore Jobs): Fiber Restore \nRegion: As per Prism/MQMS\nIf the wrong region is selected then we need to delete the job and recreate it again.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(827,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 18:11:47','1605504','NC','KERNERSVILLE','IQC',1,'','Magellan Tool','Catalogs','Ensure any new changes in Support Structures, Coax, Fiber elements must be built in the same catalogues as per existing data catalogue.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(828,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 18:11:47','1605504','NC','KERNERSVILLE','IQC',1,'','Magellan Tool','Changes verification','Asbuilt Jobs - Visually inspect & verify all changes/modifications are done in Magellan as per the given SOW and Inputs.\nRestore Jobs - All support and Fiber elements build state of the respective area of Interest must be changed to NOT BUILT by disconnecting the respective area of interest.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(829,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 18:11:47','1605504','NC','KERNERSVILLE','IQC',1,'','Magellan Tool','Address Validation','All address and the LU type must be matching with PRISM and MQMS.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(830,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 18:11:47','1605504','NC','KERNERSVILLE','IQC',1,'','Magellan Tool','Support Structures','All Support structures must be selected & placed as per the latest and standard guidelines.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(831,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 18:11:47','1605504','NC','KERNERSVILLE','IQC',1,'','Magellan Tool','Fiber Elements','All Fiber elements must be selected & placed as per the latest and standard guidelines.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(832,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-21 18:11:47','1605504','NC','KERNERSVILLE','IQC',1,'','Magellan Tool','Fiber Elements','Ensure Mux Type, range and Reserved Wavelengths are match as per Fib