fter print.\n\nCheck and Verify the Restore comment call out should always be as mentioned below. \nFor restore jobs comment should be \"RESTORED\"','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3056,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:25','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',15,'','After Deliverables','Call Out properties','Check and Verify all the Callout Box (Title Block & Comment Callout) properties are as per the Project Specification/Standards. \nRectangle Box with Red Borders & yellow Fill, Text Font: Arial Narrow, BOLD & Text Size: 36.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3057,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:25','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',15,'','After Deliverables','Report','Extract the BOM report with respective layers selected from Drop down list in the BOM type list.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3058,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:25','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',15,'','After Deliverables','House counts & address','Respective House counts and address inside PRISM PCAB boundary must be present and visible on the  After PDF document which must match the data on the Magellan.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3059,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:25','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',15,'','After Deliverables','Base Layers','\"Ensure all the required layers are turned on before generating a PDF\nNote: Select \"\"Include\"\" option if the system prompts while generating a pdf.\"','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3060,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:25','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',15,'','Deliverables Naming Format, Final Folder format & contents','After Print','After Print Naming should be as per below Naming standard.\nPRISM ID_BUSINESS NAME_AFTER_FIBER\nHybrid jobs need 2 separate packages (1 for COAX & 1 for Fiber)','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3061,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:25','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',15,'','Deliverables Naming Format, Final 