.0','Ajith V'),(3086,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','MQMS','Timer','Ensure to start the timer, while creating the assigned job in Magellan.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3087,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','MQMS','Timer','If the job is being rejected back to customer for any reason make sure to record time (a few minutes) on MQMS','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3088,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','MQMS','Route Module','Aerial and UG lengths must always be updated as \"0\" in Route module in MQMS.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3089,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','MQMS','Route Module','Ensure to submit the route module in MQMS after the modifications are done for support and addresses in Magellan, post which timer must be started on respective module','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3090,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','MQMS','Coax + Fiber Module','Post completion of Route Module, timer must run in Fiber Module until the job is ready for submission to Internal QC. (Applicable Fiber only jobs) \nPost completion of Route Module, Submit the COAX Module and run the timer in Fiber module until the job is ready for submission to Internal QC. (Applicable for COAX-Fiber jobs)','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3091,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','MQMS','Fiber Module','Fiber Module must not be submitted to Package Prep Module on MQMS untill IQC is completed.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3092,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','PRISM','Project Status','Project status in the survey tab must be \"ACTIVATED\" for all as-builts jobs.\nProject status in the survey tab must be \"CANCELLED\" for all Restore jobs.\nIf it doesn\'t match we need to prepare a Query document and send it to QG Design Supervisor/PMO and seek clarification','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3093,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','PRISM','Data Operations Name','We must update \"Lopez, Robert V - p2728875\" name in the Data Operations field on PRISM under Design Tab.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3094,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','PRISM','Design Received','Once the Data Operations field is populated with the respective name (as mentioned above) we must click the \"Design Received\" button in the Design tab.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3095,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','PRISM','Designer Name','Please input the respective QuadGen designer name from in the Designer Name field in Design Tab.\n Ensure this name must match with the name on MQMS.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3096,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','PRISM','Assign Designer','Once the Designer Name is populated, user must click on \"Assign Designer\" Button in Design Tab.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3097,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','Input Validation','Input Files','On PRISM User must navigate to Documents Tab,  Survey document   section and download the file which will has name as \"Asbuilt\" and the attachment type must be \"As-built\". \n\n\"Please note: The file must be of latest date with ASBUILT attachment type.\nIf there is no Asbuilt file under survey document section, reach out to your supervisor for confirmation on rejecting the job.\"','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3098,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','Input Validation','Input Files','Downloaded inputs files are legible, readable and clear to understand. \nIf the files are corrupted and unable to understand, then prepare a Query Document and reach out to QG Design Supervisor/PMO and seek clarifications.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3099,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','Input Validation','Input Files','Please verify and Ensure the Fiber information is available or not. (Fiber information: Hub Info, Tie point, Mux info etc.)\nIF AUDIT/SPLICING SHEET is not available please reject the job','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3100,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','Input Validation','Inputs Comments','Please verify and ensure that Comments mentioned in PRISM Design tab must be Inline with the associated SOW. \nIf it doesn\'t match we need to prepare a query document and send it to QG Design Supervisor/PMO and seek clarification.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3101,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','Input Validation','AutoCAD Validation','If the Asbuilt input file is an export from AutoCAD tool and contains AutoCAD symbols then we need to follow the flow chart as mentioned in the reference document.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3102,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','Input Validation','Restore Jobs Input files','We have to review all Design Deliverables as Inputs for Restore Jobs\n\nIf it doesn\'t match we need to prepare a query document and send it to QG Design Supervisor/PMO and seek clarification.','Yes','','100.0','Ajith V'),(3103,'Testing ATX AS-Built','2023-09-22 16:01:37','673315','SC','HILTON HEAD ISLAND','Self QC',16,'','Before Print','Layers','Ensure Coax Layer is Unchecked before taking the export for Before Print file for all FIA (Fiber only) Jobs.','Yes'